SECTION 2. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 63-1-176(c)(9), is amended by
deleting the language "A school counselor or school psychologist" and substituting instead the
language "A school counselor, school psychologist, or school social worker".
SECTION 3. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
